See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ChocoConstraint
    An interface to describe a constraint implementation for the solver.
    ChocoConstraintBuilder
    Interface to specify a builder that create a ChocoConstraint from a specific Constraint.

    Specify the choco implementation of an objective
